@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Referral";
}

<section class="subpage-bg">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <div class="titile-block title-block_subpage">
                    <h2>Referral</h2>
                    <p> <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index"> Home</a> /Referral</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="main-block">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 responsive-wrap">
                <div class="full-blog">
                    <div class="blog-content">
                        <div class="blog-text">
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                WasherKart India Private Limited offers a referral program to our customers, shops, and drivers, allowing them to earn rewards for referring their friends, family, or acquaintances to our platform. Here's how our referral program works for each of these parties:
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Program for Customers:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                Customers can access their unique referral link through our app or website. They can share this link with their friends and family via social media, email, or any other messaging platform. When someone signs up using the customer's referral link and places an order on our platform, the customer will receive a reward in the form of a discount or cashback.
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Program for Shops:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                Shops that have a tie-up with WasherKart India Private Limited can refer other shops to join our platform. When the referred shop joins and starts providing services through our platform, the referring shop will receive a reward in the form of a commission or other benefits.
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Program for Drivers:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                Drivers who are associated with WasherKart India Private Limited can refer other drivers to join our platform. When the referred driver joins and starts providing services through our platform, the referring driver will receive a reward in the form of a commission or other benefits.
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Limitations:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                Referral rewards may be subject to certain limitations or restrictions, as determined by WasherKart India Private Limited. The referral program terms and conditions may vary for each party, and they can access the details through our app or website.
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Validity:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                The referral link or program will remain valid for a specific period, as determined by WasherKart India Private Limited. After the expiry of the referral link, customers, shops, or drivers may not be able to earn any referral rewards for the referrals made through that link.
                            </p>
                            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                                Referral Program Changes:
                            </blockquote>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                WasherKart India Private Limited reserves the right to modify or terminate our referral program at any time without prior notice.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">
                                If you have any questions or concerns regarding our referral program, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@washerkart.com">mailto:support@washerkart.com.</a>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>